sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant P as prepare_initial_context
    participant L as lookup()
    participant C as cg_research
    participant I as cg_interrupt
    participant UI as UI / caller
    participant S as summarize_context
    participant A as agent

    U->>P: First buyer-search request
    P->>L: Resolve company reference
    L-->>P: Optional lookup_result
    P->>C: Run context generator
    Note over C: Required web_search_preview inside Responses API
    C-->>I: Target summary and closed questions
    I-->>UI: interrupt payload
    UI-->>I: User clarification answer
    I-->>S: Updated _cg_messages
    S-->>A: Hidden _agent_context
    A-->>A: Decide answer or search_hybrid
